{"tid":2027691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"兩會期間，原來今日北京天降異象，白晝宛如黑夜，請咁多位風水大師入","createTime":"2020-05-21T13:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T00:14:23.000Z","uid":161374,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f8902443093efded99b33e788097c1d8e4fb5168","tid":2027691,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:11:30.000Z","msg":"有冇大師可以講解下？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共政協十三屆三次會議今（21）日下午3時正式開幕，不過，明明是白天，北京的天空卻黑壓壓一片，宛如黑夜，這也是歷屆兩會中罕見的天候現象，根據中國氣象局的官方預報指出，北京除了有雷陣雨，還有大風等強對流天氣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-05-21/410126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-05-21%2F410126&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoVxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=cc74ca2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-05-21/410126</a>"},{"pid":"524015674e059a50494b5b06230c5d633fc13a0e","tid":2027691,"uid":32347,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f8902443093efded99b33e788097c1d8e4fb5168","tid":2027691,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:11:30.000Z","msg":"有冇大師可以講解下？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共政協十三屆三次會議今（21）日下午3時正式開幕，不過，明明是白天，北京的天空卻黑壓壓一片，宛如黑夜，這也是歷屆兩會中罕見的天候現象，根據中國氣象局的官方預報指出，北京除了有雷陣雨，還有大風等強對流天氣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-05-21/410126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-05-21%2F410126&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoVxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=cc74ca2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-05-21/410126</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:13:54.000Z","msg":"可能北京啲霧霾咋"},{"pid":"cc75ebf02876ce2686f3fe8a3c4ce773edd02621","tid":2027691,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"524015674e059a50494b5b06230c5d633fc13a0e","tid":2027691,"uid":32347,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f8902443093efded99b33e788097c1d8e4fb5168","tid":2027691,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score